1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
She did not know — the Emperor had written two decrees for her. One reward. One death.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
She only knew — one demon remained in the cold palace. Deep within the dry well.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Three days ago — beyond the stone bed, she sensed a thread of demonic aura.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Faint as a candle in the wind — yet its quality was staggering. A blade in its sheath.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Three days later — she was ready.

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Xiao He — whatever you hear tonight, do not come out.

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Guard the well. If I don't return in half an hour — go to the Empress Dowager.

8
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:51,000
The well dropped over ten zhang. She slowed her fall — landed soundlessly.

9
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Bones. Rubble. The Snake Demon's lair — already stripped.

10
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:05,000
She walked past the stone bed — into a narrow passage choked with black moss.

11
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:12,000
A hundred paces in — the passage opened. An exquisite stone chamber.

12
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Night-pearls in the walls — bathing all in soft gold. At its center — sat someone.

13
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:23,000
No — not someone.

14
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:28,000
You came.

15
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:33,000
The day the Snake Demon died — I knew. I have been waiting.

16
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:41,000
The blood of the Demon Ancestor runs in your veins. You are — the heir of the Demon Emperor.

17
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:47,000
I have waited here — three hundred years.

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:52,000
You may call me — the Seal.

19
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:59,000
I am no demon. I am a Seal placed by the Ancients — and inside, sleeps the real thing.

20
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:07,000
An Ancient Demon King. Sealed here — for three thousand years.

21
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:13,000
In a hundred years — it will break free.

22
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:21,000
Reinforce the Seal — or, devour its power.

23
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:28,000
With Demon-Emperor blood — you can consume any demon's strength.

24
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:34,000
Devour it before it wakes — and you become, the new Demon Emperor.

25
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:40,000
The new Demon Emperor… I need time to think.

26
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:46,000
There is no rush — I will wait.

27
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:52,000
When she climbed out — the night had grown deep.

28
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:58,000
My lady — what's down there?

29
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:04,000
— A secret.

30
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:12,000
From this night on — her goal is no longer the cold palace. It is the throne of all demons.
